Class Item

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.copakond.sweetfluffysheep.model.utils.game.GameObject
cz.cvut.copakond.sweetfluffysheep.model.items.Item
All Implemented Interfaces:
IItem, IGameObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Coin, FreezeItem, RageItem
public class Item extends GameObject implements IItem
Item class represents an item in the game. It extends the GameObject class and implements the IItem interface. The item has a texture, position, duration, and effect. The item can be picked up and used by the player. Each item must inherit from this class.
